  "text": "This functional implementation of the presented algorithm is provided as proof of concept. This implementation is not optimized in terms of computational load. Future research to improve the algorithm itself by adopting more efficient methods [CITATION_1] is advisable. The computational load generated by the integration of the squared l 2 norm of the residual vector over the polytopes is expected to be significantly reduced.",
